  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">My Great Story: Integrated Communications Campaign for Greater Understanding on Migration Issues - Pilot in the Philippines</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Piloting in the Philippines, the proposed project aims to bridge the gap in understanding between migrants and the general public by increasing awareness of Filipino people on migration related issues. It will be done by an integrated communications campaign named &#x2018;My Great Story&#x2019;, which is centered around enhanced social media contents and supported by interactive public events. Illustrating realities of migrants and the environments they live in, the &#x2018;My Great Story&#x2019; theme aims to bring forward personal accounts and experiences of migrants, internally displaced persons; the people on the move, and convey them to the wider public in an engaging way.</narrative>
  </description>
